Gregory S. Foran 
Executive Compensation
As Executive Vice President at WAL-MART STORES INC, Gregory S. Foran  made $11,546,122 in total compensation.  Of this total $1,006,424 was received as a salary, $2,861,535 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $6,650,490 was awarded as stock and $1,027,673 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2017 fiscal year. 


