Gregory S. Foran



Mr. Gregory S. Foran is Executive Vice President & President-US Walmart at Wal-Mart Stores, Inc. and President & Chief Executive Officer-Asian Region at Wal-Mart International.
Mr. Foran was previously employed as President & Chief Executive Officer by Wal-Mart and a Director-Supermarkets, Liquor & Petrol by Woolworths Ltd.



